KOKUSAI KISEN KABUSHIKI KAISHA, Appellee, v. COLUMBIA STEVEDORING CO., Inc., Appellant. No. 57. Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. Dec. 5, 1938. Mengel & Conroy, of New York City (Carl K. Mengel and George A. Conroy, both of New York City, of counsel), for appellant. Crawford & Sprague, of New York City (George C. Sprague and Nicholas J. Healy, III, both of New York City, of counsel), for appellee.

Before L. HAND, SWAN, and CHASE, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Judgment, 23 F.Supp. 403, affirmed.
